trans-unit.source: Defines column-specific properties that apply to <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Grid"></xref> elements.
trans-unit.target: Definerer kolonnen egenskaper som gjelder for <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Grid"> </xref> elementer.

trans-unit.source: ColumnDefinition uses its own special structure, a <xref:System.Windows.GridLength>, to describe its width characteristics.
trans-unit.target: ColumnDefinition bruker sine egne spesielle strukturen en <xref:System.Windows.GridLength>, for å beskrive egenskapene bredde.</xref:System.Windows.GridLength>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.GridLength> allows a ColumnDefinition to support variable distribution of available space.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.GridLength>tillater ColumnDefinition å støtte variabelen distribusjon av tilgjengelig plass.</xref:System.Windows.GridLength>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that represents the actual calculated width of a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som representerer faktiske beregnet bredden på en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This property is a calculated value that is based on other width inputs and the layout system.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er en beregnet verdi som er basert på andre bredden inndata og oppsettet-systemet.

trans-unit.source: When you add or remove rows or columns, the ActualWidth for all <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition> elements and the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.RowDefinition.ActualHeight%2A> of all <xref:System.Windows.Controls.RowDefinition> elements becomes zero until <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.Measure%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: Når du legger til eller fjerne rader eller kolonner, ActualWidth for alle <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition>elementer og <xref:System.Windows.Controls.RowDefinition.ActualHeight%2A>av alle <xref:System.Windows.Controls.RowDefinition>elementer blir null før <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.Measure%2A>kalles.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement.Measure%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.RowDefinition> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.RowDefinition.ActualHeight%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Double> that represents the actual calculated width in device independent pixels.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Double>som representerer faktiske beregnet bredden i enheten uavhengig piksler.</xref:System.Double>

trans-unit.source: The default value is 0.0.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er 0,0.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that represents the maximum width of a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som representerer maksimumsbredden for en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: When you use these values together in the same code example, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition.MinWidth%2A> value takes precedence over the MaxWidth value, which in turn takes precedence over the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition.Width%2A> value.
trans-unit.target: Når du bruker disse verdiene sammen i det samme kodeeksemplet den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition.MinWidth%2A>verdien overstyrer MaxWidth-verdi som i sin tur overstyrer den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition.Width%2A>verdi.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition.Width%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition.MinWidth%2A>

trans-unit.source: When you add or remove rows or columns, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition.ActualWidth%2A> for all <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition> elements and the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.RowDefinition.ActualHeight%2A> of all <xref:System.Windows.Controls.RowDefinition> elements becomes zero until <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.Measure%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: Når du legger til eller fjerne rader eller kolonner, den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition.ActualWidth%2A>for alle <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition>elementer og <xref:System.Windows.Controls.RowDefinition.ActualHeight%2A>av alle <xref:System.Windows.Controls.RowDefinition>elementer blir null før <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.Measure%2A>kalles.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement.Measure%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.RowDefinition> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.RowDefinition.ActualHeight%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition.ActualWidth%2A>
